-- Turkey's Bank Asya shares extend losses to trade down 20 percent
-- By Seda Sezer
-- Mon Sep 15, 2014 07:16AM EDT
-- None



ISTANBUL, Sept 15 (Reuters) - Shares in Turkish Islamic lender Bank Asya <ASYAB.IS> fell 20 percent to 0.99 lira on Monday, extending earlier losses, as trading resumed after a suspension of more than a month.

